---
title: Purple Sweet Potato Nicoise with Black Olive Vinaigrette
description: We took some liberties with the classic salad Niçoise, but worry not, this salad is worthy in its own right. Vibrant purple sweet potato and hearty chickpeas marry with traditional components like tomatoes and green beans for an unexpectedly harmonious medley. The entire salad is amped up by an intensely flavorful black olive vinaigrette. Bon appétit!
